With Cloudy, planning your day-to-day activities is easier than ever before. 
See the current temperature, hourly forecasts for the next 48 hours and a 7-day forecast for locations around the world. 
Easily find all the weather information you need to plan your life with confidence. Rain, storm or shine: Plan your day, week or even your next vacation with the right tools and insights at your fingertips. 
• Planning an adventure? Check the forecast so you don’t get caught in the rain. 
• Quickly find all the weather data you care about in one place! 
• Beautifully designed, simple to use. 

INSIGHTFUL DETAILS: 
 - Today's Min, Max temperature; 
- Adjustable weather layouts — choose which weather parameters you’d like to see first; 
- Precipitation and humidity info; 
- Wind speed;
- Sunrise/Sunset and Moonrise/Moonset time; 
- Current local time.

Don't let bad weather take you by surprise! 
You won’t even have to look out the window as Clody will make you feel like you are already outside! 
Weather can change instantly – anytime, anywhere. Therefore, download the weather app NOW with notable features and keep an eye on detailed weather updates.
